    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/3b795f20f2b0f0b34c4f368cfad2390d.poster.avif?t=1763680257\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/3b795f20f2b0f0b34c4f368cfad2390d.webm?t=1763680257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/3b795f20f2b0f0b34c4f368cfad2390d.mp4?t=1763680257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super reaKtor</strong> is a fast-paced Bullet Hell with original controls, where you must survive by collecting energy pellets, and avoid or absorb hostile TRI-SKL bullets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUT WHAT MAKES IT SPECIAL?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE CONTROLS</strong>: You can Move, Rotate, but also change the Size of your laser beam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE GAMEPLAY</strong>: Your weak points are located on the sides of your laser beam. Your central beam can absorb hostile bullets !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/68532bebf6112332d75f4114e4e2231e.poster.avif?t=1763680257\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/68532bebf6112332d75f4114e4e2231e.webm?t=1763680257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEMO FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LIGHT DISCOVERY MODE :</strong> Discover 72 patterns in the three first levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARDS :</strong> Compete with the world and your friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRISKELS :</strong> A lot of them. Almost too many.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULL GAME FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARCADE MODES :</strong> 3 major game modes, Over 500 hand crafted patterns across 5 levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARDS :</strong> Compete with the world and your friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRAINING MODE :</strong> Master the patterns in a safe zone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ACHIEVEMENTS :</strong> Collect them all</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRISKELS :</strong> A lot of them. And we still add some.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/2008cba0ff1512be845edeff962acb20.poster.avif?t=1763680257\" width=780 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/2008cba0ff1512be845edeff962acb20.webm?t=1763680257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094240/extras/2008cba0ff1512be845edeff962acb20.mp4?t=1763680257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
